com.persistit.exception

Class PersistitIOException

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception
        • com.persistit.exception.PersistitException
          • com.persistit.exception.PersistitIOException
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CorruptJournalException

    public class PersistitIOException
extends PersistitException
    This is a wrapper for an IOException. It is convenient for the caller of a Persistit method to catch PersistitExceptions without also needing to catch IOExceptions.
    Version:
    1.0
